Revision history for Alien-TidyHTML5

v0.3.0    2018-10-29 21:24:29+00:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
  - Improved the alienfile configuration, to fix #1 (Graham Ollis).

  [Incompatabilities]
  - Renamed "exe_file" to "exe".

  [Bug Fixes]
  - Undid the check for alternative package names, #2 (Graham Ollis)

v0.2.0    2018-10-28 14:24:32+00:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
  - Look for alternative package names, "tidy5" and "tidy-html5", #1.

  - Add exe_file method to return the path of the tidy executable, #2.

  [Toolchain]
  - Bumped prerequisite version for DZ plugin.

  - Explicitly specified a minimum Perl version.

  - Update distribution metadata.

v0.1.1    2018-10-25 17:50:49+01:00 Europe/London
